imdb.plot outline: An original street style fashion series from A-List Content. My Street Style is a weekly fashion series where everyday fashionistas break down their trendy looks, including how they shop for and rock their favorite gear. Learn about new trends, how to shop them and wear them all in one place. My Street Style is equal parts style guide and and how-to. When you hear the tagline "These are my streets, and that's my style" you're watching the original My Street Style.
